{"id": 2817, "genre": 1002, "title": "测测你在互联网上的路见不平指数", "description": "多了块屏幕，你的正义指数上升了吗？（题图来自：istock © CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 9597, "comment_count": 66, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190308173027SDVh02LQGAp3qZm4.jpg", "page_style": 0, "question_style": 1, "category": 4, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-08T17:00:40Z", "column": null, "gender_question": {"id": 5454, "content": "你的性别", "genre": 4, "position": 1, "options": [{"id": 330304, "title": "男", "content": "", "image": null}, {"id": 330305, "title": "女", "content": "", "image": null}], "image": null}, "slide_question": {"id": 5455, "content": "你觉得你的网络路见不平指数为", "genre": 3, "position": 1, "max_score": 10.0, "options": [{"id": 331967, "title": "只看看不说话", "content": "吃瓜群众路过", "image": null}, {"id": 331968, "title": "一声吼", "content": "总得做点什么声援一下", "image": null}], "image": null}, "normal_questions": [{"id": 5477, "content": "你曾经因为一个明星/陌生网友的负面消息，到ta的微博下指责ta吗？", "genre": 1, "position": 1, "options": [{"id": 331945, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 8, "image": "img/option/option/20190308091507f8MRi1VG72sp9gaT.jpg"}, {"id": 331946, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 92, "image": "img/option/option/20190308091551H0foDTebzu94qRc2.jpg"}], "image": null}, {"id": 5478, "content": "你曾经留言指出过某篇文章的事实错误或错别字吗？", "genre": 1, "position": 1, "options": [{"id": 331947, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 42, "image": "img/option/option/20190308091627iPX1w0ykzhA7GVTf.jpg"}, {"id": 331948, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 58, "image": "img/option/option/20190308091637UA9KQ4RdTNJWHt2p.jpg"}], "image": null}, {"id": 5479, "content": "看到一则“施暴者无罪，见义勇为者入狱并赔偿”的新闻时，你更可能", "genre": 1, "position": 1, "options": [{"id": 331949, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 25, "image": "img/option/option/20190308091715Uz9eVtKpjLa074lW.jpg"}, {"id": 331950, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 75, "image": "img/option/option/20190308115336Kir2J3yMBVvNuCps.jpg"}], "image": null}, {"id": 5480, "content": "看到社交网络上好友求助（捐款/寻人/寻狗）时，你更可能会", "genre": 1, "position": 1, "options": [{"id": 331951, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 20, "image": "img/option/option/20190308091940DrMegFTjHiaIZnkP.jpg"}, {"id": 331952, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 80, "image": "img/option/option/20190308091954caF5pTYSnu0P6hd4.jpg"}], "image": null}, {"id": 5481, "content": "看到家庭群里的谣言文，你会", "genre": 1, "position": 1, "options": [{"id": 331954, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 28, "image": "img/option/option/20190308092032dCk7V6xglufKDc3B.jpg"}, {"id": 331955, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 72, "image": "img/option/option/20190308092045eYV9M6FQJB5pgEq3.jpg"}], "image": null}, {"id": 5482, "content": "在微信上看到一篇抄袭文/洗稿文，你更可能", "genre": 1, "position": 1, "options": [{"id": 331956, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 21, "image": "img/option/option/20190308092111bQFo7juyeCVlzgqk.jpg"}, {"id": 331957, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 79, "image": "img/option/option/20190308092121RYyF1ixAGbeBmqlQ.jpg"}], "image": null}, {"id": 5483, "content": "有人在社交网络上发布自杀状态，你更可能", "genre": 1, "position": 1, "options": [{"id": 331958, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 19, "image": "img/option/option/201903080921536jSvnGRca3TuwMF5.jpg"}, {"id": 331959, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 81, "image": "img/option/option/20190308092200jfdmaXGPscVKv7hH.jpg"}], "image": null}, {"id": 5484, "content": "看到一个陌生网友的自拍留言区被很多杠精毫无理由地喷时，你会", "genre": 1, "position": 1, "options": [{"id": 331960, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 14, "image": "img/option/option/20190308092236cVzgyPSiUCTBle5W.jpg"}, {"id": 331961, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 86, "image": "img/option/option/20190308092246uHNC3XQ6K2jedxFr.jpg"}], "image": null}, {"id": 5485, "content": "看到朋友转发一则虚假广告，你的反应更可能", "genre": 1, "position": 1, "options": [{"id": 331969, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 27, "image": "img/option/option/20190308100425jWf1zPGmQtDBMAYN.jpg"}, {"id": 331970, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 73, "image": "img/option/option/20190308100435JqRFur2ZWYtLN6z8.jpg"}], "image": null}, {"id": 5486, "content": "看到商家带有歧视意味的宣传语（“男朋友看漫威，女朋友请勿打扰”），你更可能", "genre": 1, "position": 1, "options": [{"id": 331987, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 18, "image": "img/option/option/20190308174928bs1tyR8q4xHIgD9L.jpg"}, {"id": 331988, "title": "", "content": "", "percent": 82, "image": "img/option/option/20190308110941s9AWMV1Z8w4b5ilv.jpg"}], "image": null}]}